        <p>1.1.1.The company Habesha Sport Betting p.l.c., registred in Ethiopia, Addis Ababa with address: Addis Ababa, Kirkos, Woreda 02, House No.: 464/303; company TIN 0053189137, under Sport betting license issued in accordance with sport betting license directive no.: 83/2005. License no.: 0014/2009 (hereinafter referred to as “the company“) operates the sports betting website www.HABESHABETS.com (hereinafter referred to as “internet sportsbetting“).</p>
        
